PURPOSE:

To implement Confidentiality and Authentication in secure file sharing.

PERCENT COMPLETE:

100 %


TO COMPILE:

Steps to run the program,
1) UnZip file. (tar -xvf Project.tar)
-----------for Indexing Server -----------
1) cd IndexingServer
2) make
------------For each peer -------------
1) Open new terminal
2) cd Peer<IndexNumber> (e.g. Peer1, Peer2) (Note - Open seperate terminal for seperate Peers)
3) make


TO RUN:
-----------for Indexing Server -----------
1) java Server <Port Number>

------------For each peer -------------
1) java Peer<IndexNumber> <Port Number> (e.g. java Peer1 3500)


COMMANDS:

-------------- To get a file -------------
On peers terminal type 
1) get <FileName>

------------ To Refresh ------------------
1) refresh

--------------To exit ----------------
1) exit

--------------To do nothing ----------
1) type anything 


SAMPLE OUTPUT:

----------------- ON INDEXING SERVER ---------------
bingsun2% java Server 3500
server listing on port  3500
Waiting for connection
